io.github.pulsebeat02.minecraftmedialibrary

Class LibraryPathHandle

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.pulsebeat02.minecraftmedialibrary.LibraryPathHandle

  • public class LibraryPathHandle
extends java.lang.Object
    A simple class to handle all the paths the library uses to store configuration files, audio files, video files, and other necessities used throughout the library.
